text: Fred Guillermety (2 June 1918 - 4 August 1965) was a Puerto Rican sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:1965 deaths Category:Puerto Rican male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Puerto Rico Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from San Juan, Puerto Rico
